node.text:
Night Owl is back on the track today and we feel complete again. 🦉Catch @chaseelliott9 burning that rubber at @indianapolismotorspeedway! 🏁

Go to your nearest Hooters and get the race day bundle while you’re at it. Fried pickles and a pitcher of @mountaindew or @buschbeer Light for just 15 bucks!

*Available at participating locations.
Cannot be combined with other offers.
